OL,3,CScottish Fire and Rescue paying
OL,4,C'buckets of money' due to staff
OL,5,Csickness
OL,7,FScotland's Fire and Rescue Service is
OL,8,Fpaying "buckets of money" to a private
OL,9,Fcompany to run its wellbeing
OL,10,Fdepartment ` because so many staff
OL,11,Fmembers are off sick or have quit.
OL,13,FITV Border can reveal that Heales
OL,14,FMedical is providing key services
OL,15,Fbecause of absences and resignation.
OL,17,FIt follows our investigation earlier
OL,18,Fthis year, which revealed that one in
OL,19,Ffive people working for the fire
OL,20,Fservice had either experienced or
OL,21,Fwitnessed bullying or harassment.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@YO]
