OL,7,FSimon Macfarlane, of the trade union
OL,8,FUnison, said: "We know there's a real
OL,9,Fissue with the culture in the Scottish
OL,10,FFire and Rescue Service and that's
OL,11,Fevident in the wellbeing department
OL,12,Fbecause it's certainly not living up
OL,13,Fto his name.
OL,15,F"Our members have taken tribunals,
OL,16,Fthey've left employment and they've
OL,17,Fput in a collective grievance."
OL,26,@pD@OOUwD@AOUyD@_O]
