OL,7,FHe said an internal investigation had
OL,8,Fbeen carried out into how wellbeing
OL,9,Fservice was run and making changes to
OL,10,Fservice as a result.
OL,12,FHeales were initially brought in to
OL,13,Fhelp deal with firefighters and staff
OL,14,Fmembers' records failing to meet "the
OL,15,Frequired standard".
OL,17,FThis was in November and the firm's
OL,18,Fremit has expanded significantly as
OL,19,Fworkers in the occupational health
OL,20,Fdepartment were signed off or quit
OL,21,Faltogether.
OL,26,@vD@bOUwD@RO]
