OL,7,FMacfarlane added: "We're meeting the
OL,8,Fservice (on Thursday) to discuss pay
OL,9,Fand I can anticipate they'll be
OL,10,Ftelling us they don't have enough
OL,11,Fmoney.
OL,13,F"Yet there's buckets of money going
OL,14,Fout the door to Heales to provide a
OL,15,Fservice that there are staff ` our
OL,16,Fmembers ` trained and well equipped to
OL,17,Fdo.
