OL,7,F"If we want to keep firefighters safe,
OL,8,Fit's better having staff who are
OL,9,Fmotivated by public service than
OL,10,Fprivate profit to do that work."
OL,12,FIn April, an ITV Border investigation
OL,13,Funcovered a "toxic" culture and a
OL,14,Fseries of concerns around
OL,15,Fdiscrimination and harassment which
OL,16,Fhas worsened in recent years.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@`O]uD@MOUuD@SO]
