OL,7,FMultiple frontline firefighters and
OL,8,Fcivilian staff have raised concerns
OL,9,Finternally either through formal
OL,10,Fgrievance procedures, informally
OL,11,Fnotifying managers or in some cases
OL,12,Fsubmitting dossiers chronicling
OL,13,Finstances of individuals being
OL,14,Ftargeted in ways that were perceived
OL,15,Fas being unfair.
OL,17,FAt that time, first minister John
OL,18,FSwinney said he was "concerned" by the
OL,19,Freport and urged the fire service to
OL,20,Faddress the concerns.
OL,26,@zD@UOUzD@_O]
