OL,7,FA report was published on Wednesday by
OL,8,FHM Fire Inspectorate in Scotland about
OL,9,Fthe service's culture.
OL,11,FIt made a series of recommendations
OL,12,Fand "areas for consideration" and
OL,13,Ffinished by saying: "We would
OL,14,Fencourage the service, its managers
OL,15,Fand commanders to consider clearly
OL,16,Farticulating and acknowledging,
OL,17,Fthrough relevant communication, that
OL,18,Feveryone's contribution is equally
OL,19,Fimportant and valued."
