OL,7,FBrian Whittle, the South Scotland MSP
OL,8,Fand Conservative public health
OL,9,Fspokesman, said: "There's a certain
OL,10,Firony that the people who are supposed
OL,11,Fto keep people in the fire and rescue
OL,12,Fsafe are the ones that are off ill at
OL,13,Fthe moment.
OL,15,F"It is a worry. It speaks to a wider
OL,16,Fproblem, it speaks to stress, it
OL,17,Fspeaks to strain on the system, it
OL,18,Fspeaks to the cuts that have been made
OL,19,Fto the system over a period of time by
OL,20,Fthe SNP."
