OL,7,FFiona Ross, the fire service's
OL,8,Fdirector of people said: "During an
OL,9,Faudit of our health assessment
OL,10,Frecords, we identified a number of
OL,11,Frecords which did not meet the
OL,12,Frequired standard.
OL,14,F"We have notified all colleagues whose
OL,15,Frecords are impacted. An in-depth
OL,16,Frecovery plan is being implemented,
OL,17,Fand we are taking steps to ensure this
OL,18,Fdoes not happen again.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUvD@AOU
