OL,7,FShe added: "We have built upon an
OL,8,Fexisting working relationship with
OL,9,FHeales Medical to assist us in this
OL,10,Fprocess.
OL,12,F"We explored options with other
OL,13,Fexternal providers. However, due to
OL,14,Fthe vast size of the SFRS and
OL,15,Fgeographical spread, it has been
OL,16,Fdifficult to find providers to support
OL,17,Fthe full extent we require."
